feat: Enhance file download and thumbnail handling
- Refactor file download handler to improve error handling and response management. - Update thumbnail handler to provide dynamic responses based on file metadata. - Introduce a new DownloadResult type to encapsulate download metadata. - Implement signed download processing with improved signature validation. - Enhance folder tree retrieval to include expiration for download links. - Add support for generating signed download URLs with customizable expiration. - Update file model to include thumbnail URL in API responses.
